Package file_handling

Contains the Classes used for the File Handling (Import / Export CSV) and the management of the database credentials in an external file
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabaseCredentialsManager
    A class for managing the database credentials in an external file so that they may be retrieved easily.
    FileHandler
    Class for Import and Export Handling of CSV and GEOJson Files
    SessionManager
    An object used to save and load sessions.
